programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - The Return (Part 1)

programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - The Return (Part 2)
programme.desc: Season 3, Episode 11 O'Neill and Woolsey, the lone survivors of the replicators' bloody coup, hide out in an abandoned section of the city. Knowing Landry has an order to nuke Atlantis if a foothold situation should ever arise, the two lay low awaiting their fate.

programme.title: Stargate Atlantis - Echoes
programme.desc: Season 3, Episode 12 Teyla begins to see apparitions of ancients in distress and believes they are the ghosts of the Ancients recently massacred by the Replicators. McKay believes he's found the whale that saved him a year ago while trapped in a submerged puddle jumper.

programme.title: Stargate Universe - Common Descent

programme.title: Stargate Universe - Epilogue
programme.desc: Season 2, Episode 18 Returning the settlers to their home planet Novus, the Destiny crew discover the planet has been abandoned and is on the verge of seismic destruction. While pouring through an underground archive, the crew learns of the true origins of Novus.

programme.title: Stargate Universe - Blockade
programme.desc: Season 2, Episode 19 When Destiny’s attempt to recharge in a star is foiled by attacking drones, Eli suggests a risky plan to recharge in a super-hot blue giant…a star so hot it could destroy the ship…unless someone stays aboard and keeps the ship under manual control.

programme.title: Stargate Universe - Gauntlet
programme.desc: Season 2, Episode 20 After a battle, Destiny’s only option for survival is a jump to the next galaxy. Crew members return to Earth to say what may be their final farewells before embarking on their journey. But a risky stop may put the entire plan in jeopardy.

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Crusade

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Camelot

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Flesh And Blood

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Morpheus

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - The Pegasus Project
programme.desc: Season 10, Episode 3 SG-1 travels to the Pegasus Galaxy and the city of Atlantis in hopes to find a clue to a weapon that can destroy the Ori. Starring Ben Browder, Amanda Tapping, Christopher Judge, Claudia Black, Beau Bridges, and Michael Shanks.

programme.title: Stargate SG-1 - Insiders
programme.desc: Season 10, Episode 4 The team makes a pact with an old enemy to fight their common foe, and the results are disastrous. Starring Ben Browder as Lt. Colonel Cameron Mitchell, Christopher Judge as Teal'c, and Amanda Tapping as Lt. Colonel Samantha Carter.
